page.title: 10INDUSTRY
page.content: trailers.They own 24 acres of land and they have in the warehouses every kind of alcoholic drink you can think of and Moulinex goods.The large lorries travel about 40,000 miles a year and the small lorries travel 20,000 miles a year. There is a factory called Coolers owned by Mr. Burgess who has 18 acres of land.It sells frozen fruit and vegetables and was built in 1804. Rawlings is a building contractors who construct any type of building and sell them.Their office is just off The Square.They employ 17 people in the office and 25 people outside.They have been here about 9_10 years. Fosters has been here 2 and a half years and is a family business. They get out 20 orders a week which range from 500 to 500,000 and they print a variety of products e.g.calendars and cards.
